# JIT Gapless Audio Transcoding

Implement gapless audio transcoding in JitTranscoder using the proven approach from SegmentEncoder.server.ts - separate audio/video encoding with FFmpeg concat demuxer for precise sample-level trimming.

## Test plan / verification steps

**Primary verification through automated tests:**
1. Enhanced JIT transcoder tests (add to existing file):
   ```bash
   npm test lib/transcode/src/jit/JitTranscoder.test.ts
   ```
2. Audio timing utilities tests (paired with source file):
   ```bash
   npm test lib/render/AudioTiming.test.ts
   ```

**Manual verification (secondary):**
- Generate consecutive audio segments and verify no clicks/pops at boundaries
- Test with audio analysis tools to verify sample-perfect alignment
- Verify segments can be concatenated at filesystem level without re-encoding

